<p class="abstract hayMasTexto">With the U.S. tiptoeing&hellip;</p><div class="completeText"><p>With the U.S. tiptoeing toward the end of the lockdowns, people will be driving more than they have in the past year, for work and for play, and O&#039;Reilly Automotive stock should be one winner, Teresa Rivas writes in this week&#039;s edition of Barron&#039;s. The company has used the downtime caused by the pandemic to improve its business and gain market share, while expanding its bricks-and-mortar footprint, the author notes, adding that work should pay off in the months ahead as life continues to return to something like normal. <a class="reference_link" href="https://www.barrons.com/articles/americans-are-driving-again-oreilly-automotive-stock-should-be-a-winner-51618486200?mod&#61;past_editions" target="new">Reference Link</a></p></div></dd> </div><div class='elementosRelacionadosWrapper '> <div class='clickeable toggleRelated'> <span class='showWord'>Show</span><span class='hideWord'>Hide</span> Related Items&nbsp;<span class='showWord'>>></span><span class='hideWord'><<</span> </div> <div class='relatedContent'> <ul class='globalRelated'> <li class='linkRelTopic_1'> <a href='#rel_1_tab'>Company News</a></li> <li class='linkRelatedRecs'> <a href='#rel_rec_tab'>Street Research </a></li> <li class='linkRelTopic_2'> <a href='#rel_2_tab'>Earnings</a></li> <li class='linkRelTopic_3'> <a href='#rel_3_tab'>On The Fly</a></li> <li class='linkRelatedEvents'> <a href='#rel_ev_tab'>Events </a></li></ul><div class='relTopic1' id='rel_1_tab'><section class="infoCompany"> <span class="ticker symbolInsideNews" data-ticker="ORLY">ORLY</span> <span class="infoCompany">O'Reilly Automotive</span></section><section class="statsCompany"> <dl> <dt>$530.48 / <p class="companyPrice gain">+8.3<small class="smallWithoutIcon"> (+1.59%)</small></p></dt> </dl></section><section class='recsCompany'><dl class="hot related" data-id="3273438" data-sd="2021-03-26 09:23:23"> <dt> 03/26/21</dt> <dd